    "description": "Are you a skilled Senior Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? Amazon India in Ghaziabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Amazon India:\nAmazon India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Amazon India!",
